        fax 33 1 69 15 65 86


===============================================================
The LogiCal Team at INRIA Rocquencourt 
	http://logical.inria.fr 
is offering a engineer position to collaborate to the development 
of the Coq Proof assistant http://coq.inria.fr 

Tasks 
	- organization of the documentation/FAQ/on-line help/WEB site
	- re-organization, documentation interface of the libraries
	- profiling of the system
	- stabilizing the installation procedure on different platforms

Prerequisites :
	- formal methods, logic
	- programming in ML
	- English

Dead-line for application is May 30th. 

The job should start no later than September 1st. 
The position is for one year with a possible extension to 18 months.
Salary depends on the qualification.

